    <item>
      <title>Docs: Skip</title>
      <link>https://groupe-edf.github.io/watchdog/docs/quickstart/skip/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://groupe-edf.github.io/watchdog/docs/quickstart/skip/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;Developers have the option of skipping checks on certain commits with the expression &lt;code&gt;[skip hooks.rule.condition]&lt;/code&gt;. The expression is valid at&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rule, for example: Ignore security rules of type &lt;code&gt;Secret&lt;/code&gt; &lt;strong&gt;[skip hooks.security.secret]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handler, for example: Skip all &lt;code&gt;security&lt;/code&gt; rules &lt;strong&gt;[skip hooks.security]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All Handlers &lt;strong&gt;[skip hooks]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;Example&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;$ git commit -am &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;chore: add dummy configuration file [skip hooks.security.secret]&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
$ git commit -am &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;chore: add dummy configuration file [skip hooks.security]&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
$ git commit -am &lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;chore: add dummy configuration file [skip hooks]&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Or even better with &lt;a href=&#34;https://git-scm.com/docs/git-push#Documentation/git-push.txt--oltoptiongt&#34;&gt;Push Options&lt;/a&gt; to keep git history clean &lt;strong&gt;Under development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;$ git push -o security.secrets.skip
$ git push -o hooks.skip&lt;span style=&#34;color:#666&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#b44&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;security.secrets,tag.semver&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#080;font-style:italic&#34;&gt;# Comma separated handler.rule&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
      </description>
